cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving the performance of deep object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper focuses on improving the region proposal step and the object recognition step, which are both related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of pre-training, which is a common technique in deep learning (cs.MM). Finally, the paper reports results on several benchmark datasets, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE).
